snippet.title: AMAZING Sandbox Survival! - The Superfluous Sand [Alpha] | S1E1
snippet.description:
Here I present to you; a one in a million sandbox survival game, made by the one and only Voided Pixels. Hope you enjoy the gameplay!

-
There is no commentary since there are reasons why I am not going to commentate. I'll list a few: I'm not an English native speaker since I am born in the Netherlands, though my grammar isn't that bad.

Information about the game:
This game is made by Voided Pixels. The game is in its Alpha state, and yet it has so much to offer! It has lots of content and features, I can assure you that with the release of the game, this game will have an endless amount of things that you can do in the game.

This game has surprised me several times with its features, and I'm someone who doesn't often play a game for a very long time, but I sure did in this one!
If released (which is far from now) it will cost money, but I really recommend buying it!

To download the game (for free) you just have to visit the site: 
https://voidedpixels.itch.io/superfluous-sand
When you have clicked the "Download now" button, you can either donate (by typing in a price) or download the game for free (by clicking "No thanks, just take me to the downloads").
